propriete.name: order_inf_is_transitive
propriete.forme: all (x : self) (y : self) (z : self)!order_inf(x, y) -> !order_inf(y, z) -> !order_inf(x, z)

propriete.name: geq_transitive
propriete.forme: all (x : self) (y : self) (z : self)!geq(x, y) -> !geq(y, z) -> !geq(x, z)

propriete.name: order_compatible_with_cancellation
propriete.forme: all (x : self) (y : self) (z : self)!leq(!plus(x, z), !plus(y, z)) -> !leq(x, y)

propriete.name: order_compatible_with_plus
propriete.forme: all (x : self) (y : self) (z : self)!leq(x, y) -> !leq(!plus(x, z), !plus(y, z))

propriete.name: total_order
propriete.forme: all (x : self) (y : self)!leq(x, y) or !leq(y, x)

propriete.name: leq_transitive
propriete.forme: all (x : self) (y : self) (z : self)!leq(x, y) -> !leq(y, z) -> !leq(x, z)

propriete.name: order_sup_is_supremum
propriete.forme: all (x : self) (y : self) (i : self)!order_sup(i, x) -> !order_sup(i, y) -> !order_sup(i, !sup(x, y))

propriete.name: order_sup_is_transitive
propriete.forme: all (x : self) (y : self) (z : self)!order_sup(x, y) -> !order_sup(y, z) -> !order_sup(x, z)

propriete.name: order_inf_is_infimum
propriete.forme: all (x : self) (y : self) (i : self)!order_inf(i, x) -> !order_inf(i, y) -> !order_inf(i, !inf(x, y))
